# Give V4L2 video nodes (our usbip-attached UVC webcam) perms the camera HAL can
# open. WSA's ueventd has no /dev/video rule, so nodes default to 0600 root:root
# and the cameraserver-uid external HAL gets EACCES. ueventd applies this when the
# node is created — atomically, before the HAL's inotify watcher tries to open it.
/dev/video*               0660   cameraserver   camera
